  • SEARCH: 
 

Uses of Package
msp.simulator.environment

  • Packages that use msp.simulator.environment 
    Package Description
    msp.simulator
    MSP Numerical Simulator - Main package.
    msp.simulator.dynamic
    Dynamic Engine of the Simulation.
    msp.simulator.dynamic.forces
    This package implements all of the linear interaction between the environment and the satellite.
    msp.simulator.dynamic.guidance
    Gather all of the guidance services and processing method, i.e. the attitude law of the satellite over time.
    msp.simulator.dynamic.propagation
    This package gather all of the objects responsible for processing a controlled propagation of all of the satellite defined states through the environment.
    msp.simulator.dynamic.torques
    Provide all of the models and tools to efficiently handle the contribution of any torque on the satellite over the time.
    msp.simulator.satellite
    The Satellite package represents the overall satellite object in the simulation.
    msp.simulator.satellite.assembly
    The assembly of the satellite is responsible to set up and maintain all of the components and services related to the satellite body, states, etc.
    msp.simulator.satellite.sensors
    This package gathers all of the sensor modules of the satellite.
